Basically what is happening is there is no out of zone communication. You can only talk to people in the same area (zones arent called zones in DAoC). You have a little chat box with 5 tabs on it. Main] Broadcast]Guild] Group] Friends] you click on whatever tab to talk to that group of designated people. So you can have chat groups where you dont have to type /reply or /r to talk, you just type it into the chat box.<P>--------------------<P><B>Quasi Moto</B><BR><I>Defender of Albion</I><BR><B><A HREF="http://ordoequester.hypermart.net/" TARGET=_blank>Ordo Equester</A></B><BR>=========================================<BR><B>Achiever</B> <I>80%</I> <B>Killer</B> <I>80%</I> <B>Explorer</B> <I>26%</I> <B>Socializer</B> <I>13%</I> | <B>Rational:</B><I> NT</I><BR>=========================================<BR><B><I>"It is not the end, It is not even the beginning of the end. It is the end of the beginning"</B></I><BR>           <A HREF="mailto:MFresh@antisocial.com">MFresh@antisocial.com</A> 
